                    <span>I worked at microsoft for 2 years and the win32 api was some big secret. Well now that I got ahold of this book it's no longer secret. Hansen did an awesome job of explaining how windows really works. Windows is no longer a secret. I would have given it stars but I just started so it will be a while before I can give 5 stars</span>
                  
              
